sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Web
    participant API
    participant DB

    User->>Web: Open catalog
    Web->>API: GET categories/items
    API->>DB: Load catalog
    DB-->>API: Catalog data
    API-->>Web: Active catalog

    alt Item quote
        User->>Web: Choose item/options
        Web->>API: GET item detail
        API->>DB: Load enabled options
        DB-->>API: Item detail
        API-->>Web: Item and options
        Web->>API: POST cart/quote
    else Combo quote
        User->>Web: Choose combo/picks
        Web->>API: GET combo detail
        API->>DB: Load combo choices
        DB-->>API: Combo detail
        API-->>Web: Slots and products
        Web->>API: POST cart/quote
    end

    API->>DB: Resolve current prices
    DB-->>API: Price data
    API-->>Web: Quote

